rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0002
rows.name: I never dreamed we'd be found out here.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0003
rows.name:
17 years went by, and
no one found us...

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0004
rows.name:
If we don't stop him here, the
Iiran army will be all over us.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0005
rows.name:
If we don't stop him now,
he'll set the army on us.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0006
rows.name:
You're right... I guess
we have to do it.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0007
rows.name: Let's head back to Felt Village.
